title: 이달의소녀탐구 #92 (LOONA TV #92)
summary:
MV Filming starts in Hong Kong!
0:02 -- HyunJin big eyes pouty expression. Why you makin’ that face HyunJin?
0:05 -- “Fighting!” Haseul leads the group in a rousing cheer.
0:13 -- “I want to film an earring commercial,” classic HyunJin line.
0:15 -- HyunJin blocks the sun.
0:25 -- HeeJin gives Vivi a Korean lesson, so she can mime her part better.
(But did any of her miming to that part even make it into the final cut of the MV? Nope. Sad.)
0:45 -- Vivi complains about Korean word pronunciations, “Sa” and “Rl”
0:56 -- HeeJin thumbs up for Vivi! “I’m rooting for you Unnie!”
